N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 720-5.1 - Ordered revisions

State Regulations

When rates, charges, rules, or other tariff provisions
are prescribed by commission order, the changes shall be established by
amendments to or reissue of the affected schedule or schedules. Each affected
leaf shall bear the following notation: "Issued in compliance with order in C. (case number)
dated (mm/dd/yyyy; date of order)."
Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16

720-5.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
